CMP #$03                      ; check primary message counter again                                 ;  B
BCC IncMsgCounter             ; if not at 3 yet (world 8 only), branch to increment                 ; 
SBC #$01                      ; otherwise subtract one                                              ;  B
JMP ThankPlayer               ; and skip to next part                                               ; 
