RenderAttributeTables:                                                                              ; fun():  B
LDA CurrentNTAddr_Low         ; get low byte of next name table address                             ; 
AND #%00011111                ; to be written to, mask out all but 5 LSB,                           ; 
SEC                           ; subtract four                                                       ; 
